high_descs: Turn around and go right to the counter.
Pick up the blue plate from the counter.
Wash the plate in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the end cabinet with the toaster on it.
Put the plate in the cabinet below the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk into the kitchen then turn right and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to that counter then move to your right until you're in front of a dirty plate.
Turn around and walk to the sink that's on your right so you are standing in front of it facing it.
Wash the plate in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left and take a step.
Open the cupboard to the right of the stove and put the plate down there then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn left, turn left at the red bin, turn right to face the counter on the right.
Pick up the dirty blue plate from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the plate in the sink, wash the plate with water, pick up the plate from the sink.
Turn left and face the counter with the toaster on it and look at the cabinet below the counter.
Open the cabinet door, put the plate in the cabinet, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To clean a plate and put it in the cabinet.
